        "created_at": "2023-12-07T04:13:06.651Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This thing is so good right now. Two bottles over the past 6 months, both brilliant under Diam 10.</p>\n<p><strong>2010 Guffens-Heynen M\u00e2con-Pierreclos Tri de Chavigne</strong>: Notes of pineapple husk, custard apple, white peach and honeysuckle. Great mineral cut and delineation. Perfect balance. Youthful, with fabulous drive and length.</p>",
